Kylie Jenner shamelessly flashes her nude knickers and bra in see-through bodysuit for New York dinner date The reality babe doesn't even bother with proper clothes anymore...   Share   Comments By Zoe Shenton 04:57, 12 FEB 2017 Updated 05:01, 12 FEB 2017 Celebs Flashing her flesh: Kylie Jenner (Photo: Splash)   Share   Comments Get celebs updates directly to your inbox + Subscribe Thank you for subscribing! Could not subscribe, try again later Invalid Email Whatever Kim Kardashian can do, it appears that Kylie Jenner can do much better these days. 
The Keeping Up With The Kardashian star has now officially taken over sister Kim in the attention-grabbbing stakes.
Clearly feeling as confident as ever, the 19-year-old popped out to grab a bite to eat at trendy restaurant Nobu in a see-through nude body stocking on Saturday.
Kylie, who is in New York for Fashion Week, was flashing her nude knickers and matching bra underneath the thin layer of sheer material.
She wore the revealing look with a tan jacket and nude over-the-knee boots.
Kylie Jenner and Tyga go to dinner at Nobu in New York City, New York (Photo: Splash News) Kylie Jenner and Tyga go to dinner at Nobu in New York City, New York (Photo: Splash News) Read More Kim Kardashian reveals she's keeping all her clothes for North - including her Vogue cover shoot wedding gown She wore her dark brunette hair scraped away from her face and had her make-up applied flawlessly.
As well as sitting pretty on the FROW at various shows, Kylie will also be opening her second pop up store in the city.
Kylie Jenner and Tyga go to dinner at Nobu in New York City, New York (Photo: Splash News) Kylie Jenner (Photo: Instagram/KylieJenner) The reality star is set to open another temporary store for her beauty empire Kylie Cosmetics on Mercer street on Monday.
Last week, Kylie shared an image of the outside of the building with boards emblazoned with pink dripping liquid covering the windows to her Instagram account.
Kylie Jenner's new hair (Photo: SNAPCHAT) Kylie Jenner (Photo: Instagram) She captioned the post: "Wow can't believe I'm coming to NYC next week to open up my second Pop Up Shop.. DREAMS!!! I'll see you guys there... Address: 27 Mercer St. New York City
"When: 2/13/17 I'll open the doors at 10am that morning & will be open daily until 9pm! (sic)."
